Ingredients 1 fresh ginger, chopped into slices 8 cups of water 1 teaspoon of honey or sweetener. Lemon juice Recipe • In a pot, add the chopped ginger, honey and water and bring to a boil • Once boiled, turn off the heat and cover the pot to allow it steep • Once cool, pour in a cup and mix with lemon juice. Source: https://www.food.com/recipe/trentens-ginger-tea-cold-and-stomach-remedy-390045